message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to offer you this fantastic product. Given its value and features, I believe a starting price of $15,000 is fair. What are your thoughts?
Hello Alice, thank you for the offer. I understand the value of the product, but I am only able to pay up to $10,000 for it. Would you consider this price?
Bob, thanks for your offer. I understand your position, but $10,000 is significantly below what I can accept. Could you consider $13,500? It's a compromise, recognizing its value to both of us.
Alice, thank you for your response. I appreciate your offer, but I am still unable to go above $10,000. I hope we can come to an agreement closer to my budget.
